            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]#孩子发热这些常见误区要避免#】医生介绍：儿童感染呼吸道疾病后，①发热是一种症状。多数情况下，发热是人体应对感染的保护机制，切忌过量混搭用药；②...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%91%E7%83%AD%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E8%AF%AF%E5%8C%BA%E8%A6%81%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%91%E7%83%AD%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E8%AF%AF%E5%8C%BA%E8%A6%81%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#孩子发热这些常见误区要避免#</span></a>】医生介绍：儿童感染呼吸道疾病后，①发热是一种症状。多数情况下，发热是人体应对感染的保护机制，切忌过量混搭用药；②<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E7%83%AD%E6%80%A7%E6%83%8A%E5%8E%A5%E5%88%AB%E6%8E%90%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%AD%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E5%8F%91%E7%94%9F%E7%83%AD%E6%80%A7%E6%83%8A%E5%8E%A5%E5%88%AB%E6%8E%90%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%AD%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#孩子发生热性惊厥别掐人中#</span></a>，让孩子平卧，保持呼吸道通畅，大多数5分钟内可缓解，严重时立即打120；③发热时多补充水分，不要给孩子捂到大汗淋漓，容易导致脱水👇🏻（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4976778377363503" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hkmo87lx8qj62fw1dgkjm02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/8Rwcq3rglx08aN200UzS01041200VlFT0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1702113288&amp;ssig=3ENISP%2BVcQ&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Gt82UtHLlx08aN1ZAcTm01041200udu00E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1702113288&amp;ssig=rqC9cmA1Td&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Gwe7bH4blx08aN21b0so01041200jDdf0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1702113288&amp;ssig=3kP8jTyDrq&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4976778377363503" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
